    "name": "Boop a Cat",
    "steam_appid": 2284680,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284680/extras/b0429458dc44d75ae42a3373fc55cfe7.avif?t=1719016274\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br>I wanted a game where there was no stress or worry.  Boop a Cat is just that, a relaxing game about booping a cat. Simple animations, hand-drawn graphics, and a clicking system to care for your feline friend.  There is much more to do in the game as well, lots of minigames and decorations to really make a unique look for your cat's home.<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284680/extras/3d3a1ff5f5923905efba79e63f9eb9b3.avif?t=1719016274\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br>Boop your cat is the first thing to do in this game!  Every boop gives you cat coins and boops that you can use to unlock hats, ties and socks for the cat to wear.  I plan to add more with each update as well as other features.<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284680/extras/dd2228e52fe2f39f77c95146f3346a39.avif?t=1719016274\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br>*Boop the Cat<br>*Dress the Cat<br>*Decorate the Cat's Room<br>*Fish<br>*Make Sushi<br>*Play Hi-Lo<br>*Catch Mice<br>*Dodge Yarn Balls<br>*Plus Much More!",
